<div class="container">
    <h2>Welcome to the Contract Monthly Claiming System</h2>

    <p>
        This system is designed to simplify and digitize the process of managing
        monthly claims for contracts. It provides a secure and user-friendly
        platform where different roles work together to ensure accurate and timely
        processing of claims.
    </p>

    <h3>Who Can Use the System?</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Lecturers:</strong> Submit claims for completed work such as
            teaching hours or contract-based tasks.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Program Coordinators:</strong> Review claims submitted by
            lecturers, check for accuracy, and approve or send back for corrections.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Program Managers:</strong> Monitor reports, track the overall
            progress of claims, and ensure compliance with institutional policies.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Human Resources (HR):</strong>
            Oversee the final approval process, generate reports, and ensure that claims align with institutional regulations. HR can also manage overall claim status, track document submission, and maintain accurate records.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Why Use This System?</h3>
    <p>
        The Contract Monthly Claiming System streamlines the workflow by:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Reducing paperwork and manual errors.</li>
        <li>Speeding up claim reviews and approvals.</li>
        <li>Providing real-time visibility into claim status.</li>
        <li>Ensuring transparency and accountability across all roles, including HR’s oversight role in ensuring compliance and final approval.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Please log in with your assigned role to continue and access your dashboard.
    </p>

    <a href="/Account/Login"><button>Log In</button></a>
</div>
